                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8880" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0217</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2529 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云天化集团全产业链运营与供应链韧性提升之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Road to Enhancement of Yuntianhua Group&#39;s Whole  Industry Chain Operation and Supply Chain Toughness</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纳超洪，王少飞，莫秋实，孙璐，杨洪丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云天化集团有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云天化集团；全产业链；供应链转型；供应链韧性；供应链安全；2024百优案例；重点项目；系列4-3</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Yuntianhua Group；whole industry chain；supply chain transformation；supply chain resilience；supply chain security</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了云天化集团供应链转型与产业链延伸的双链融合发展历程。案例详细梳理了供应链转型、产业链延伸的内在动因、具体举措以及所取得的显著成效。化肥行业原材料价格不断上升、产品同质化严重、产能严重过剩，云天化集团产业链耦合度低、供应链韧性不足以及管理风险高，使得云天化集团2016年之前连续三年巨额亏损。为此，云天化集团自2016年起依托已有的化肥产业和商贸业务，开始开展供应链转型延伸产业链，供应链模式经历了“1.0-传统贸易商模式”“2.0-供应链服务商模式”和“3.0-产业链运营商模式”，成功实现了从“商贸、化肥企业”向“供应链企业”的转型发展。同时，云天化集团还结合管理会计狠抓精益管理、运用数字技术实现业财数据“可视化”、依托国际国内市场助力双链融合，在新冠疫情、俄乌冲突、巴以冲突等外部不确定因素冲击下，集团供应链韧性不断提升，产业竞争力持续加强，集团利润由2016年云南省国企“亏损王”提升为2023年的“盈利王”。本案例以云天化集团供应链韧性提升与全产业链运营为主线，重点阐述其供应链建设及产业链延伸等方面的应用，旨在引导案例使用者运用相关理论深入理解供应链韧性打造及其对集团运营的赋能作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study details the dual-chain integration development process of Yuntianhua Group&#39;s supply chain transformation and industrial chain extension. It meticulously examines the intrinsic drivers, specific strategies, and substantial outcomes of these transformations.Confronted with escalating raw material costs, severe product homogenization, and significant overcapacity in the fertilizer industry, Yuntianhua Group exhibited a low degree of industrial chain coupling, inadequate supply chain resilience, and high management risks, leading to substantial losses for three consecutive years prior to 2016. Consequently, starting in 2016, Yuntianhua Group leveraged its established fertilizer industry and trading operations to embark on supply chain transformation and industrial chain extension. The supply chain model progressed through phases of &quot;1.0-Traditional Trader Model,&quot; &quot;2.0-Supply Chain Service Provider Model,&quot; and &quot;3.0-Industrial Chain Operator Model,&quot; successfully transitioning from a &quot;trade and fertilizer company&quot; to a &quot;supply chain enterprise.&quot;Concurrently, Yuntianhua Group emphasized lean management through the integration of management accounting, harnessed digital technology to achieve the &quot;visualization&quot; of financial and operational data, and leveraged both international and domestic markets to facilitate dual-chain integration. Despite external uncertainties such as the COVID-19 pandemic, the Russia-Ukraine conflict, and the Israel-Palestine conflict, the group&#39;s supply chain resilience has continually improved, its industrial competitiveness has consistently strengthened, and its profitability has risen dramatically, transforming from the &quot;loss leader&quot; among Yunnan state-owned enterprises in 2016 to the &quot;profit leader&quot; in 2023.This case study centers on Yuntianhua Group&#39;s enhancement of supply chain resilience and comprehensive industrial chain operations, with a focus on its supply chain construction and industrial chain extension initiatives. It aims to guide academic researchers in applying relevant theories to gain a deeper understanding of the development of supply chain resilience and its enabling role in enhancing the group&#39;s operational performance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链韧性；全产业链；协同效应理论；战略管理；供应链管理；产业组织理论；风险管理；双链融合；可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
